# ── Policy (revised 2026-07-19) ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Deploys are an explicit allowlist (deploy.yml: built dist/ + data/ + the stub
# copy list), so tracked docs and tooling can never leak onto the site. The old
# gitignore-as-deploy-exclude-list role is retired. KNOWLEDGE IS TRACKED:
# task lists, plans, agent prompts/guides, and generation scripts belong in
# docs/ and scripts/. Only regenerable caches, machine-local state, and
# secrets stay ignored below.

# Regenerable raw-source caches (large, re-downloadable; the committed
# intermediates in data/commentary/cow-sources/ are what synthesis consumes)
working/catena-src/
working/devotionals-raw/

# Agent per-chapter work dirs (COW synthesis loop); build junk, never deployed
scratchpad/

# Local reference material (not part of the site)
Z-ExtraResources/

# Claude Code local config / session memory (machine-specific)
.claude/
memory/

# Secrets / credentials
.env*
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
secrets.*
credentials.*
*.secret
.git-credentials*

# Astro
/.astro/
